    <summary>A free, simple, lightweight and customizable tool for desktop organization on Windows.</summary>
    <description>Declutter your digital life. Unlock the power of productivity with **Portals: Desktop Organization** — where clutter-free desktops become a reality.

## Screenshot
![Screenshot](https://cdn.statically.io/gh/Aurocosh/chocolatey-packages/master/automatic/portals/img/screenshot.png)

## Customize to your heart's content

Pretty much everything is customizable. Change colors, fonts, borders, margins, header position, icon sizes and even use images as backgrounds if you wish.

## Organize your way

Set the header position, keep the portals minimized, use custom or pre-defined sort orders and even have multiple tabs linked to separate folders in the same portal allowing you to organize exactly how you want.

## Features

* **Desktop Portals** — Create Portals on your desktop to display the contents of selected folders directly on your desktop, unlocking productivity without clutter.
* **Lightweight** — Minimal resource usage. Portals runs efficiently in the background without slowing down your system.
* **Deep Customization** — Customize size, position, colors, transparency, fonts, icon sizes, borders, margins and much more.
* **Per-Portal Overrides** — Make each Portal unique by overriding specific settings (colors, fonts etc.) per-portal.
* **Layouts** — Save sets of Portals into layouts, which can be applied automatically as your display setups change.
* **Settings Profiles** — Save the customizations you create as settings profiles and quickly switch between them. Even link them to your layouts.
